" Remapping adapté au BÉPO

" hint sur e pour plus d’ergonomie
bind e hint
bind E hint -b

" [HJKL] -> [CTSR]
bind t scrollline 10
bind s scrollline -10
bind c scrollpx -200
bind r scrollpx 200

bind T scrollpage 0.5
bind S scrollpage -0.5
bind C back
bind R forward

" [CTSR] -> [HJKL]
unbind j
bind k fillcmdline tab
bind K fillcmdline taball
bind h fillcmdline open search
bind H fillcmdline tabopen search
bind l reload

bind o fillcmdline tabopen

bind gn tabnew
bind gb tabprev
bind gé tabnext
